chart.name: Requests/Connection
chart.programText:
A = data('nginx_vts_server_requests_total', filter=filter('code', 'total'), rollup='latest').delta().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'active'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).publish(label='C')

chart.description: Total number of RPCs completed on the server, regardless of success or failure
chart.name: # of Gitaly RPCs

chart.description: Average of request processing times including upstream in seconds
chart.name: Upstream Request Time

chart.description: Number of connections in reading headers, waiting to send response, and writing response states
chart.name: Active Connection States
chart.programText:
A = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'reading'), rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'writing'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')
C = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'waiting'), rollup='latest').publish(label='C')

chart.description: Day-over-Day Change in Requests
chart.name: Requests/sec 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('nginx_vts_server_requests_total', filter=filter('code', 'total'), rollup='average').rateofchange().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B-1).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.description: Number of builds in pipeline processing queues
chart.name: Build Pipeline Processing Queues
chart.programText:
A = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_queue'), rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_finished'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')
C = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_success'), rollup='latest').publish(label='C')
D = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:ci_build_schedule'), rollup='latest').publish(label='D')

chart.description: Latency of build related pipeline processing queues

chart.programText:
A = data('sidekiq_queue_latency*', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_queue'), rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('sidekiq_queue_latency*', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_finished'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')
C = data('sidekiq_queue_latency*', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_success'), rollup='latest').publish(label='C')
D = data('sidekiq_queue_latency_seconds', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:ci_build_schedule'), rollup='latest').publish(label='D')
